#: includes/i18n/class-wpsg-frontend-strings.php:696
msgid "Access-Request Retention (days)"
msgstr "访问请求保留（天）"

#: includes/i18n/class-wpsg-frontend-strings.php:697
msgid "Visitor access-request records (including emails) older than this are purged weekly. Set to 0 to keep indefinitely."
msgstr "超过此时长的访客访问请求记录（包括电子邮件）将每周清除。设为 0 则无限期保留。"

#: includes/i18n/class-wpsg-frontend-strings.php:698
msgid "Audit-Log Retention (days)"
msgstr "审计日志保留（天）"

#: includes/i18n/class-wpsg-frontend-strings.php:699
msgid "Audit-log entries older than this are purged weekly. Set to 0 to keep indefinitely — audit trails are kept by default for accountability."
msgstr "超过此时长的审计日志条目将每周清除。设为 0 则无限期保留——审计日志默认保留以确保可问责性。"
